      "description": "A solid, budget-friendly vehicle that offers dependable transportation and excellent value. This car shows normal wear consistent with age and use, but it remains a practical choice for daily driving, commuting, or a first-time buyer. Clean presentation, comfortable ride, and an affordable entry point make this one well worth a look.",
