    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, affordable ride without the big price tag? This car is a great value for someone who wants dependable transportation with plenty of life left to give. It\u2019s in fair condition, so it\u2019s not perfect, but it starts up, gets you where you need to go, and offers a comfortable, practical driving experience. A nice option for a daily driver, first car, or backup vehicle. Priced fairly and represented honestly by a seller who believes in keeping things straightforward.",
      "price": 21950.0,
