      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Well-kept driver with strong road manners, a smooth powerband, and a drivetrain that feels composed and responsive. This car presents as an honest, fair-condition example that has clearly been used as intended, with good mechanical feel and the kind of proven dependability that makes it easy to enjoy right away. A great option for someone wanting a capable, budget-friendly vehicle with solid bones, confident performance, and plenty of life left.",
