    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true everyday classic with the kind of presence that still turns heads, this car has a seasoned, lived-in charm that gives it real personality. It\u2019s the sort of ride that feels right at home on the daily commute, weekend errands, or as a practical project to make your own. The styling has confidence, the cabin offers familiar comfort, and there\u2019s a simple appeal here for anyone who appreciates value with character. If you want affordable transportation with a little story already built in, this one is easy to like.",
      "price": 18950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
