      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A smart value for anyone seeking dependable transportation, this vehicle offers solid everyday usability, a comfortable ride, and the kind of honest condition that makes it an appealing budget-friendly choice. It shows the normal signs of age you\u2019d expect, but it presents well, runs well, and delivers practical ownership at an attractive price point. If you want a straightforward, affordable vehicle backed by a reputable seller, this is one worth a close look.",
