    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Clean, dependable ride that\u2019s ready to be someone\u2019s solid daily driver. It shows the normal signs of use you\u2019d expect for its age, but it still starts up, drives well, and has plenty of life left for the next owner. If you\u2019re after practical, affordable transportation without the big price tag, this one is a great fit. Priced to sell and worth a look.",
